recommendations: Spikes nodding. Scales haline margined. Infrequent, on moss-peat-sedge hummocks, in burned over marshy area, mile 56. No sphagnum. Dominant plants are Betula glandulosa and Larix. Also some Potentilla, Myrica, Salix spp. standing water between hummocks. Other plants include Smilacina trifolia, Juniperus horizontalis, Arctostaphylos rubra, Rubus aff. articus. All plants growing on hummocks.
